<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN232-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉai avar pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN232">
<l>illā kiyarō kālai mālai</l>
<l>yallā kiyaryāṉ vāḻu nāḷē</l>
<l>naṭukaṟ pīli cūṭṭi nārari</l>
<l>ciṟukalat tukuppavuṅ koḷvaṉ kollō</l>
<l>kōṭuyar piṟaṅkumalai keḻīiya</l>
<l>nāṭuṭaṉ koṭuppavuṅ koḷḷā tōṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let them be nothing, morning [and] evening.</l>
<l>The days I live, let them be naught.</l>
<l>Though I adorn [his] herostone with peacock feathers [and] shed</l>
<l>a small vessel of fibre-filtered [toddy], will he take [it]?</l>
<l>Though I give it along with the land to which belong</l>
<l>glistening mountains with high peaks, he won’t take it.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
